    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"6a537097-62f7-40fe-b267-a3b838076b2c\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p><span class=\"confluence-link\">See  </span><a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661383/Depth+of+Field\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661383\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Depth of Field</a> for RenderMan depth of field.</p></div></div><p><br/></p><p>To enable depth of filed, turn on RenderMan RIS ROP's <strong>Rendering | Depth Of Field</strong>: Enable Depth Of Field.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/rfh_enableDOF.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=611&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644900/rfh_enableDOF.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644925\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_enableDOF.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644900\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"dc4e3b21-a4e3-43f0-b1df-2acc47e188fd\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/rfh_enableDOF.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=871&amp;height=356 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/rfh_enableDOF.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134268&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=611&amp;height=250 1x\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p>To change the camera properties such as Focus Distance and F-Stop, adjust them in the Camera's <strong>Sampling</strong> Tab as well as in the RenderMan controls for the added properties like <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544644871/Bokeh\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644871\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Bokeh</a>.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/camerafstop.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=532&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644900/camerafstop.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644919\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"camerafstop.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644900\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"091da157-a167-49ee-a10d-2b30d275a6c3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/camerafstop.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=573&amp;height=269 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/camerafstop.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=532&amp;height=250 1x\"></span></p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/rfh_rmanDOFEnable.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=540&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544644900/rfh_rmanDOFEnable.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544644922\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_rmanDOFEnable.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544644900\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7ed61907-2c17-447c-9bb5-0b4dd2528583\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/rfh_rmanDOFEnable.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=860&amp;height=398 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544644900/rfh_rmanDOFEnable.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433134039&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=540&amp;height=250 1x\"></span></p>"
